Name: Buffet Liberty - Tôn Đức Thắng
Address: 17 Tôn Đức Thắng, P. Bến Nghé, Q. 1

Phù hợp: Tiếp khách, tiệc công tu, gia đình, họp nhóm, sinh nhật…
Món đặc sắc: Sashimi, Sushi, Tempura, Món nướng Yaki kiểu Nhật, Mì Udon…
Điểm đặc trưng:
- Vị trí đắc địa trung tâm quận 1, không gian Nhật Bản ấm cúng, có máy lạnh.
- Món ăn mang hương vị chuẩn Nhật, giá thành hợp lý.

Mô tả tiện ích: Bãi xe gần nhà hàng (Phí phụ thuộc đơn vị trông giữ xe)

My first experience of Teppanyaki and it was delicious. Watching the chef was mesmerizing and his dishes melted in your mouth.
Các món ăn thật tuyệt vời! Bạn có thể thư giãn và thưởng thức khiêu vũ trong khi ăn tối. Rat khuyen khich.

I was many time visiting the outlets of wraps & rolls In different locations in Vietnam 
Love it. Easy to eat and taste so fresh

On previous visits to Vietnam, this was a go to place because of the extensive menu catering to most requirements and pretty cheap cost. It was always great value for money and was quality food. So this visit we made our way here…Unfortunately, either of the owners have changed or their desire has changed because the food was greasy, smaller quantities and generally not enjoyable. Unfortunately I will not go here again.
ランチタイムに利用しました。メニューが豊富でまた価格もリーズナブルで気軽に食事をすることが出来ました。朝７時から22:30までの営業という事で朝食からディナー、そしてアルコールを楽しむ事が出来ると思います。僕たちもビールとDalat Wine White ダラットワインを頂きました。
